title: SIS Deli and Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Organic, Buffet, Salad bar, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Serves mostly organic food to eat in or take out. Offers a weekday breakfast buffet, as well as a salad lunch buffet, of which the salad buffet has several vegan selections. Additionally also vegan cupcakes, raw food biscuits and more are available.
